Penelope Cruz, 47, set pulses racing in a short pink minidress at this year's Oscars Luncheon, which was held yesterday. She attended the event alongside her husband Javier Bardem, 53, where she put her legs on full display at the star-studded event. The beauty wore her hair sleek and straight and her tresses flowed down on her shoulders. The actress put wore an eye-catching dress that had button details and woven material. Her look was stylish and sophisticated as she posed for pictures.  Meanwhile, her other half Javier has also been nominated for an Oscar this year, in the category of Best Actor. 